original_text:
Ages ago I was set up,
    at the first, before the beginning of the earth.
korean_text: 만세 전부터, 태초부터, 땅이 생기기 전부터 내가 세움을 받았나니

sentences.original_text: Ages ago I was set up
sentences.korean_translation: 나는 아주 오래 전에 세움을 받았다

sentences.original_text: before the beginning of the earth.
